"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"그날 쪽지에 나는 이렇게 적었어.\n「히나랑 제대로 대화할 수 있기를」 ……이라고.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event21-06-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"히나","body":"……!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event21-06-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"그 소원을 별이 이루어 줄 리가 없어.\n이루는 건 나 자신이라고…… 그렇게 자각도 하고 있었어.\n그러기에 이전보다 너하고 같이 있는 기회를 만들고자 했어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event21-06-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"그렇게 하면 쪽지의 소원도 이루어질 거라고 생각했으니까.\n……하지만 네 연주를 듣는 것만큼은 계속 피해왔어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event21-06-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"그러던 중, 오랜만에 네 연주를 들었는데……\n네 소리는 기술에 구애받지 않는 매력적인\n소리라고, 그렇게 느꼈어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event21-06-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"「음악을 즐기고 있다」 ……나한테는 없는 그런 소리가 났어.\n네게 지지 않기 위해서 무엇에도 좌우되지 않는 평가를 받고 싶어서\n기술을 연마해왔는데.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event21-06-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"내 소리 따위는…… 그만큼 「시시한 소리」였다는 걸\n확실히 느끼고 말았어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"pui01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event21-06-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"네게 지고 싶지 않아……\n그것 하나만을 위해서 쳐 오던 기타 소리 같은 건\n시시한 소리가 나는 게 당연하겠지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event21-06-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"이젠…… 이젠 전부 싫어. 「시시한 소리」를\n계속 연주하는 나 자신도, 쪽지에 적은 소원으로부터\n점점 멀어져가고 있는 나 자신도 전부…… 전부!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"angry02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event21-06-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"히나","body":"언니는…… 언니는 거짓말쟁이야!!!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event21-06-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"뭐……?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event21-06-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"히나","body":"언니, 약속했잖아?\n우리는 서로가 기타를 시작한 계기니까 멋대로 기타를 그만두거나\n하지 않겠다고!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event21-06-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"히나","body":"나는 그게 엄청 기뻤는데……!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"cry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event21-06-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"히나","body":"나는 언니의 기타 소리, 엄청 좋아! 전보다도 지금이\n훨씬 더 룽하고…… 그러니까……\n즐거운듯한 소리를 하고 있는걸? 자기는 모르는 거야?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event21-06-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"히나","body":"나는 언니의 기타 소리를 시시한 소리라고\n생각한 적 없어! 언니의 소리를 듣고서\n나도 기타를 시작한 거라고!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"serious02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event21-06-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"히나……!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event21-06-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"히나","body":"내가 모르는 사이에 언니한테 엄청 많이\n상처를 줬구나. 정말 미안해, 언니.\n하지만…… 나는 언니가 기타를 그만두지 않았으면 좋겠어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event21-06-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"히나","body":"어떤 이유라도 좋아! 괴로운 게 있다면 내 탓으로 해도\n괜찮아. 언니가 기타를 계속할 수 있다면 얼마든지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event21-06-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"히나","body":"나는 예전처럼 언니랑 다시\n친해지고 싶다고 생각했어. 하지만 그 탓에 언니가\n괴로워진다면……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event21-06-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"히나","body":"……괜찮아. 나를 싫어하더라도.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"cry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event21-06-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySo